# AI-Driven Correlation of Cybersecurity Telemetry & Transactional Behaviour

## Overview

This project uses Artificial Intelligence to detect suspicious financial transactions by correlating cybersecurity telemetry with transactional behavior.

## Features

- Login anomaly detection
- Failed login monitoring
- High-value transaction analysis
- New device detection
- AI anomaly detection using Isolation Forest
- Flask web interface

## Technologies

- Python
- Flask
- Scikit-learn
- Pandas
- NumPy

## Run

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Train model

```bash
python train_model.py
```

Run application

```bash
python app.py
```

Open

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```
